# Proposal: On-Chain Dice Game vApp

## Author
- GitHub: @putra-122

## Category
- Gaming

## Description
A simple on-chain dice game where players roll a dice (1–6) and their scores are stored on-chain.  
A leaderboard tracks the highest scores among players.  
This project demonstrates the gaming potential on the Soundness Layer.

## Technical Architecture
- Frontend: Web dApp (React + Tailwind).
- Backend: Smart contract (testnet).
- Flow:
  1. Player connects wallet.
    2. Clicks "Roll Dice".
      3. Contract generates a random number 1–6.
        4. Player’s score is updated on-chain.
          5. Leaderboard can be displayed.

          ## Example Pseudocode
          ```solidity
          contract DiceGame {
                mapping(address => uint256) public scores;

                    function rollDice() public {
                                uint256 dice = (uint256(keccak256(abi.encodePacked(block.timestamp, msg.sender))) % 6) + 1;
                                        scores[msg.sender] += dice;
                    }

                        function getScore(address player) public view returns (uint256) {
                                    return scores[player];
                        }
          }
                        }
                    }
          }